🚨Schedule Update!!🚨

We’ve made some changes by adding another climbing session for the UTCC community to enjoy!! 🧗 Mark your calendars with the new times and come crush it with us💪

New Climbing Schedule:

New Climb Sessions:
• Wednesday: 8:30-10:30 AM @ Basecamp QW
• Thursday: 8-11 PM @ Basecamp QW
• Friday: 8-11 PM @ Basecamp QW
• Sunday: 12-3 PM @ Basecamp BW

Same fun, more chances to climb! 🎉 See you on the wall! 🧗‍♀️
Come climb with us! ND is collaborating with the UofT Climbing Club to host a bouldering social! 30% discount, limited spots left. Link in our bio for more information!

At our next Monday run, we will be joined by the UofT Climbing Club @uoftclimbs! 🪨 🧗‍♀️ The UofT Climbing Club offers climbing-oriented socials, such as bouldering, top rope, and outdoor climbs! They will give a short talk at the beginning on what they do, but the rest of the run will remain the same and as always, is open to everyone. Come find out what they do or just come for our regular 5k run!

If you are a member/exec of a club/student group at UofT and are interested in being showcased at the UTRC, feel free to send us a dm or an email (universityoftorontorunclub@gmail.com)
first outdoor trip of the year just dropped! sign up with link in bio while there’s still space besties!
